data.name: TextBox1.Text
data.value: We sell parts that are compatible with building robots over a large range of complexity. While a clawbot is featured in the “schematics” page, users have also made specially designed combat robots that square off against one another in an arena and RC cars with line trackers that follow designated paths around a specified area. The possibilities are endless and a great way to teach your kids (or yourself) about mechanics and programming.
